description: Erection of two additional floors at roof level and the extension, alteration and conversion of part of the existing plant at sixth floor ground level of Westgate House to provide 51 residential units. The erection of an eight-storey building providing 26 flats on the western part of the site. A total of 77 apartments are proposed. The proposal provides 145 cycle parking spaces, 22 onsite parking spaces and amenity space.
